snippet.title: Falskaar Announcement Trailer - A Skyrim New Lands Mod
snippet.description:
Falskaar is now available on the Skyrim Nexus here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37994/?

The announcement is finally here! Falskaar is my current mod project for The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim. It adds a whole new land full of quests, people, places, things to do, and much much more!

It's being worked on tirelessly, and will be fully voiced! My goal for release is Early 2013.

You may view the WIP thread on the Bethesda Softworks forums at: http://forums.bethsoft.com/topic/1398650-trailerwip-falskaar-thread-2/

For more updates and info please subscribe to this channel and like my facebook page at: http://www.facebook.com/pages/Alexander-J-Velicky/215460455198174

The song is Empathy by Hania Lee . It was used under a non-commercial free license, so thank you Hania for making your music available to everyone! You may listen to and download the song at: http://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/327466
